ARTICLE.TITLE: Strait of Hormuz
ARTICLE.TEXT: A Navy official says a U.S. ship was forced to change course and move out of the way of Iranian fast boats while moving through the Strait of Hormuz during the weekend, in what has become a frequent occurrence there.
